{"tid":555229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新北加一分]【恐怖意外】七旬翁頭顱遭挖泥機鏟中 身首異處慘死","createTime":"2018-02-09T08:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T08:46:06.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"14785d0912c9b47938c8fcda6846add61317417d","tid":555229,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180209/57812395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180209%2F57812395&d=iQT7bkje%2BHzlp0KayH3135zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=5b5ccc4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180209%2F57812395&h=cbaeed1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180209/57812395</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣新北發生恐怖意外。今日下午，五股區成泰路一段一處砂石場，周姓挖泥機操作員(25歲)，正在場內開挖砂石時，不慎將一名撿拾回收廢物的林姓男子（75歲）頭顱<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鏟下</span>。<br />\n<br />\n林男身首分離當場慘死，轄區警獲報迅速趕抵，目前現場以封鎖現場取證，並依林男所騎乘電單車，循線找尋家屬到場指認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}